      },
      "date": "2011-08-06 16:34:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e8c0e3ea-c049-11e0-8bdf-52540025f9af).  Ran 5 tests.  No failures.",
